00:15:42,350 --> 00:15:43,560
All hail...
- King Yudhishthir!

127
00:15:44,490 --> 00:15:46,470
All hail...
- King Yudhishthir!

128
00:15:53,350 --> 00:15:54,520
Her Highness,
my daughter...

129
00:15:56,590 --> 00:15:58,570
Where is my daughter Vrushali?

130
00:16:20,290 --> 00:16:21,260
Look over there.

131
00:16:21,450 --> 00:16:22,430
Who has been washed up
on the shore?

132
00:16:23,420 --> 00:16:25,520
It is some woman.
Let's go.

133
00:16:26,520 --> 00:16:28,260
Yes, let's go.

134
00:16:35,290 --> 00:16:38,320
Oh! She is the daughter
of Vrishbhan.

135
00:16:40,490 --> 00:16:42,490
It seems as though she is alive.

136
00:16:43,320 --> 00:16:46,270
Let us take her to the Doctor.
Let's go.

137
00:17:48,860 --> 00:17:49,840
Vrushali

138
00:17:51,060 --> 00:17:52,940
are you alright?

139
00:17:56,860 --> 00:17:57,900
Adhiratha?

140
00:17:58,860 --> 00:17:59,860
Yes, dear.

141
00:18:01,100 --> 00:18:03,970
You and Vrishbhan had
gone to Indraprastha.

142
00:18:04,860 --> 00:18:06,070
Then how did you
fall into the river?

143
00:18:15,830 --> 00:18:18,870
Serpents had attacked us
there, Adhiratha.

144
00:18:20,860 --> 00:18:21,840
Even...

145
00:18:23,000 --> 00:18:25,940
Even my father was killed!

146
00:18:31,860 --> 00:18:32,840
I...

147
00:18:33,100 --> 00:18:36,980
I fell into the river
while trying to save myself.

148
00:18:42,960 --> 00:18:44,840
Here you go.
Drink this.

149
00:19:03,030 --> 00:19:05,010
No one died,
child.

150
00:19:05,860 --> 00:19:07,860
The Pandavas have
captured the serpents

151
00:19:07,900 --> 00:19:10,000
and compelled them
to draw the venom out.

152
00:19:12,930 --> 00:19:15,030
Your father must be alive.

153
00:19:21,860 --> 00:19:22,840
Then...

154
00:19:22,900 --> 00:19:24,930
Then I should return
to Indraprastha.

155
00:19:25,800 --> 00:19:27,800
Adhiratha, I have to go
to Indraprastha

156
00:19:27,900 --> 00:19:29,030
to my father.

157
00:19:29,900 --> 00:19:30,970
I want to go there.

158
00:19:31,000 --> 00:19:32,800
Certainly, dear.
Certainly.

159
00:19:33,860 --> 00:19:35,840
Most of the subjects
of Hastinapur

160
00:19:35,960 --> 00:19:37,770
are migrating to Indraprastha.

161
00:19:38,930 --> 00:19:40,930
You may travel with any family

162
00:19:41,030 --> 00:19:42,800
you are familiar with.

163
00:19:44,800 --> 00:19:46,900
Yes.
- Let's go.

164
00:19:47,030 --> 00:19:50,740
