189
00:21:35,700 --> 00:21:37,700
not an insult to father and me?!

190
00:21:37,730 --> 00:21:39,730
It certainly is an insult,
my darling.

191
00:21:40,860 --> 00:21:43,670
It certainly is an insult.

192
00:21:44,760 --> 00:21:46,710
And it is also a major problem.

193
00:21:49,730 --> 00:21:50,830
We must stop

194
00:21:50,900 --> 00:21:55,670
these people from
leaving Hastinapur

195
00:21:55,730 --> 00:21:56,760
my darling.

196
00:22:06,830 --> 00:22:09,710
I need to meet His Highness.

